summary: This FBI electronic communication documents the transfer of case files from the Miami office to the Washington Field Office Evidence room on March 4, 2025, in the investigation of Alfredo Rodriguez. It includes an itemized list and FedEx tracking details.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez
persons.context: The case files being transferred pertain to the investigation of Alfredo Rodriguez, as indicated by the case ID and synopsis.

events.title: Transfer of case files to Washington Field Office
events.description: Case files from the Miami office in the investigation of Alfredo Rodriguez were shipped via FedEx to the Washington Field Office Evidence room.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI electronic communication dated March 7, 2025, regarding the transfer of case files.
The files pertain to the investigation of Alfredo Rodriguez (Case ID: 72-MM-I13327).
The files were shipped from Miami to the Washington Field Office Evidence room via FedEx on March 4, 2025.
The communication includes an itemized list of contents and a FedEx tracking receipt as enclosures.
